Zimbabwe Awards 20 Licenses for Coal Exploration to Boost Power Generation

-- B y   G o d f r e y   M a r a w a n y i k a
-- 
2011-09-14T09:43:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-14/zimbabwe-awards-20-licenses-for-coal-exploration-to-boost-power-generation.html
Zimbabwe awarded 20 licenses for
coal exploration and mining to help boost power generation in
the southern African country, Mines Minister  Obert Mpofu  said.  Mpofu was speaking at a mining conference today in the
capital, Harare.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Godfrey Marawanyika in Johannesburg at 
 gmarawanyika@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
